First Merged DNA sequence files & Map files must be generated by BlastDBFileGenerator.py,
then these command lines must be called.

Open Terminal in main directory and call these methods:

Building DB:
makeblastdb -in .\BlastData\db\DNA_Unified_With_TaxID.fa -taxid_map .\BlastData\db\DNA_Unified_ID_to_TaxID_mapping.fa -parse_seqids -blastdb_version 5 -title "Eykariotes DNA" -dbtype nucl -out .\BlastData\db\db_unified

Check DB status:
blastdbcmd -db .\BlastData\db\db_unified -info

Querying DB:
blastn -db .\BlastData\db\db_unified -query .\BlastData\Queries\test_query.fa -out .\BlastData\Results\test.out -num_threads 8 -task dc-megablast -outfmt 7 -evalue 1e-10 -taxids 9606 -best_hit_score_edge 0.05 -best_hit_overhang 0.25 -max_target_seqs 1
